description: Santa Monica’s favorite go-to for delicious frozen treats is Stickhouse Gelato. Expanding beyond their brick & mortar location, the Stickhouse Gelato Truck is the first to serve the streets of Los Angeles (or anywhere in the US) a selection of genuine Italian gelato on a stick, made from 100% real fruit and other all-natural & locally sourced ingredients. A few of their creamy & fruity creations include Green Tea, Tiramisu, Cheesecake, Hazelnut Dip, Mango Raspberry, Raspberry Lemon Kiwi, and so much more. Each pop contains zero preservatives, emulsifiers, artificial flavors or coloring. You’re invited to enjoy these tasty treats, completely guilt-free. If you’re looking for next your fix of refreshing frozen deliciousness, you simply must pick Stickhouse Gelato.
name: Stickhouse Gelato
